import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import Typography from '../../packages/typography/src/Typography.tsx'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"typography"}}>{`Typography`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"sizes"}}>{`Sizes`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Set font-size using `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`size`}</MDXTag>{` props.`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Typography size="h1">h1.heading1</Typography>
<Typography size="h2">h2.heading2</Typography>
<Typography size="h3">h3.heading3</Typography>
<Typography size="h4">h4.heading4</Typography>
<Typography size="h5">h5.heading5</Typography>
<Typography size="h6">h6.heading6</Typography>
<Typography size="title">普通标题!title</Typography>
<Typography size="body">主体!body</Typography>
<Typography size="button">按钮!button</Typography>`} __scope={{props,Typography}}>
	<Typography size="h1">h1.heading1</Typography>
	<Typography size="h2">h2.heading2</Typography>
	<Typography size="h3">h3.heading3</Typography>
	<Typography size="h4">h4.heading4</Typography>
	<Typography size="h5">h5.heading5</Typography>
	<Typography size="h6">h6.heading6</Typography>
	<Typography size="title">普通标题!title</Typography>
	<Typography size="body">主体!body</Typography>
	<Typography size="button">按钮!button</Typography>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"aligns"}}>{`Aligns`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Set text-align using `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`align`}</MDXTag>{` props.`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Typography align="inhert">初始状态!</Typography>
<Typography align="center">在中间!</Typography>
<Typography align="left">在左边!</Typography>
<Typography align="right">在右边!</Typography>`} __scope={{props,Typography}}>
	<Typography align="inhert">初始状态!</Typography>
	<Typography align="center">在中间!</Typography>
	<Typography align="left">在左边!</Typography>
	<Typography align="right">在右边!</Typography>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"api"}}>{`API`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"typography-1"}}>{`Typography`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Typography}/></MDXTag>
